# Step 1: Configure
    Add a Static Route, example: routing 192.168.2.0/24 & 192.168.3.0/24 via 192.168.10.13 
        sudo ip route add 192.168.2.0/24 via 192.168.10.13  
        sudo ip route add 192.168.3.0/24 via 192.168.10.13
    OR

    Set HOST as Default Gateway
        ip route del default via 192.168.10.13 dev eth0